description: Number of trees of nonempty sets with n points. (Each node is a set of 1 or more points.)
links: Index entries for sequences related to trees
formula: G.f.: B(x) - B^2(x)/2 + B(x^2)/2, where B(x) is g.f. for A036249.
crossrefs: Essentially the same as A036251. Cf. A000055, A038052.
